`indentedSyntax` is part of the `sassOptions`:

```
sassOptions: {  indentedSyntax: true  }
```

For example:
```
{
    loader: &#39;sass-loader&#39;,
    options: {
        sassOptions: {
            indentedSyntax: true
        }
    }
}
```

So - change your Webpack config to reflect that.

